# PR Packaging Checklist

- hardening_review.md contains all four required sections.
- pr_context.md contains all six required sections with non-empty content.
- pr_context.md headings match the repository pull-request template.
- All tasks in tasks.md are marked [x] including P-001, P-002, P-003.
- Key reviewer files list is explicit and high-signal (5–10 files with rationale).
- Validation Evidence references exact commands and their pass/fail output.
- Risk and Rollback notes are explicit with step-by-step rollback procedure.
- Deferred Proposals remain non-implemented with rationale and follow-up owner.
- make quality-hooks-fast passes.
- make quality-hardening-review passes.
- PR description updated to reflect final state (Open Questions section removed).
- gh pr ready <number> executed — same Draft PR, no new PR opened.
- @codex review this PR comment posted.
